| nodes |                   
nodes := SalesStrategy at: 'StratNodes'.
(nodes at: 'Kick-off Ltr') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'L';
    at: '3.Message' put: '

I won''t take much of your time.  We both know how
busy a growing business keeps you.  I''ll get to
the point.

Whizzard WORMS optical disks are available now at
a price you can afford.  Wouldn''t it be worth just
a few dollars a day for 10 GIGABYTES of PC compatible
mass storage?

I''d like to show you how you can own a WORM of your
own.  Call me to find out more about our next
educational seminar.

Best Regards,

Susan Heath
Whizzard Sales Exec';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Fol-Up Ltr';
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 7;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 2.

(nodes at: 'Fol-Up Ltr') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'L';
    at: '3.Message' put: '

There is still room for a busy executive such as yourself
at our next WORM Warmer.  Free food and drinks with a
small dose of techno-dog-and-pony at:

    The Huba Huba Room
    Slatter''s Hotel and Convention Center
    2342 Main Place

    Monday afternoon, 4:00 pm

You could add vast mass storage to your PC for just
a few dollars a day.  Join us, please.

Best Regards,

Susan Heath
Whizzard Sales Exec';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Phone Call';
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 4;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 2.

(nodes at: 'Phone Call') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'P';
    at: '3.Message' put: ' 

How are you .... NAME .... ?
This is Susan Heath of Whizzard WORMS.

Do you have a minute to talk?  Great.
Did you get my letters?
Can I pencil you in for our next seminar?';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Wake Up Ltr';  "Phone call menu overrides this default."
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 1;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 2.

(nodes at: 'Wake Up Ltr') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'L';
    at: '3.Message' put: '

You asked me to get back to you about your interest
in Whizzard WORM optical disks.

Our next WORM Warmer is this Monday afternoon at the
Huba Huba Room of the Slatter Hotel at Main Place.
I''ll call to give you details.

Thanks for you continued interest in our products.

Best Regards,


Susan Heath
Whizzard Sales Executive';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Phone Call';
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 4;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 0.

(nodes at: 'Exit Seminar') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'E';  "An Exit node"
    at: '3.Message' put: 'This customer is moving on!!';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Transfer to Seminar Strategy';
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 1;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 0.

(nodes at: 'Exit Dead Leads') info
    at: '1.Strategy' put: 'Prospecting';
    at: '2.Type' put: 'E'; "An Exit node"
    at: '3.Message' put: 'Get this dead head outa here!!';
    at: '4.Next Step' put: 'Transfer to Dead Leads';
    at: '5.Days Til NS' put: 1;
    at: '6.MTD' put: 0;
    at: '7.YTD' put: 0.

